Put the new lower wash arm in place and push it down to lock it in. Ensure it is spinning freely and does not hit the heating element. title: Access Valve 10023852

Once the dishwasher is filled to the appropriate level, the water inlet valve closes to prevent any further water from entering the tub. If the valve is faulty, you will likely experience water leakages, difficulties filling dishwasher, and poor cleaning results.
